'''Iskalonian''' was the [[Language/Legends|language]] of the peoples that inhabited the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Iskalon/Legends|Iskalon]]. In Iskalonian, children were referred to as "fry." When [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker]] and [[Leia Organa Solo/Legends|Leia Organa]] came to [[Iskalon/Legends|Iskalon]] during the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]], they were affectionately referred to by [[Primor (Inleshat)|Primor]] as both "little fry" and "smally fry."

